_sText:
Map Info: Team vs Team Battle in a foggy forest. This is the second beta released. (April 28, 05)

Bug Fixes:
* Bots dont make game lag a lot anymore.
* Bots can navigate the map better now.
* Landscape changed a bit to look less pointy.
* Added 3Dskybox with clouds.

Bugs:
* Bots are still glitchy
